---
# .gitignore 

Create `.gitignore` in root:

```gitignore
# dependencies
node_modules
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# next.js
.next/
out/

# nestjs build
dist/

# env files
.env
.env.local
.env.development
.env.production

# logs
logs
*.log

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/

# coverage
coverage/

# misc
*.pem